{"tid":1592653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登咁多偵探，不如幫手搵下呢兩個反送中最重要人物。","createTime":"2019-09-24T17:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:07:19.000Z","uid":260371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d48d68b099b4ce47ebd99741e06c5f5173d93ae6","tid":1592653,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"潘生潘太我屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n潘太唯一一次被拍到樣係喺台灣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxOXMYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxOXMYb.png&h=029690b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8BuC4O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8BuC4O.png&h=d8e74922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJ1uby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJ1uby.png&h=2dc5b489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時同佢出出入入嘅白色帽老人係潘生嘅朋友（報道話），透露潘生係三菱代理商，但潘生就係匿埋喺酒店唔見人（？）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgQCMX6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgQCMX6.png&h=107d5d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26iwRpM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26iwRpM.png&h=583f5d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/065LbpN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F065LbpN.png&h=6d17c7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8egh4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8egh4P.png&h=6554ee91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9gVyDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9gVyDa.png&h=2ddb831a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘生係香港認屍被拍到（報道話佢係潘生），咦又係戴白色帽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vekCMYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvekCMYc.png&h=d4e946f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiCJHwx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiCJHwx.png&h=3d181fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疑似潘太嘅Black Object（？）最後露面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRO5bpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRO5bpP.png&h=5eb7d1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就係反送中爆發，之後潘生潘太就只係從林奠同民建聯口中出現過，但再無現過身。<br />\n<br />\n兩個香港人幾個月嚟可以完全無被傳媒跟得到，潘生話哂有生意，理應有Office，冇理由可以為咗逃避傳媒長期唔返Office。<br />\n<br />\n都睇過其他連登仔講嘅其他可能，佢哋被禁錮，被消失。<br />\n<br />\n我都曾經試過假設去諗，香港嘅潘生潘太，可能係虛擬人物，只係林奠為咗推逃犯條例而創作。<br />\n<br />\n連登而家咁多偵探，不如真係查查佢，可能搵到核彈都唔定。"},{"pid":"dd5fbff89c6920f0297f0001921a75ec37553ce8","tid":1592653,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"3187bde9cb7914cdf86f30f5a8a45fb18aaeb96c","tid":1592653,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b9ab9d876852a2abbf14508858d17aeb2beac6","tid":1592653,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:07:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要出大量文宣講解真普選可以解決另外四大訴求，同香港長治久安<br />\n<br />\n真普選就係實現主權在民，特首權力來自於人民，特首向香港人負責，以香港人利益為先<br />\n<br />\n集中訴求 政府就唔可以分化我哋！</span></strong></span>"}]}